:<font size="15">פּרד</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
פּרד / pârad / paw-rad'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''פּרד'''

# To break through, that is, spread or separate (oneself): - disperse, [[divide]], be out of joint, part, scatter (abroad), separate (self), sever self, stretch, sunder.

